&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/USA-SEATTLE-CANLIS-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8290&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/USA-SEATTLE-CANLIS-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;USA- SEATTLE- CANLIS- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;75&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/MEDIA-GAYOT-LOGO1.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8291&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/MEDIA-GAYOT-LOGO1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;MEDIA- GAYOT LOGO&quot; width=&quot;100&quot; height=&quot;64&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;Set in a 1950 Mid-Century Modern architectural masterpiece, Canlis has been an iconic restaurant for over 60 years and remains at the forefront of the Seattle dining scene, earning James Beard Award Nomination for Best Chef Northwest 2014 and Gayot&amp;#8217;s 2014 Top 40 Restaurants in the U.S. Family owned for three generations, Canlis menu has stayed true to Pacific Northwest cuisine while progressing with a contemporary twist. A spectacular view of Lake Union and the Cascades, service is polished and elegant, always resulting in a spectacular dining experience. Jackets recommended for gentlemen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book via email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:megan@canlis.com&quot;&gt;megan@canlis.com&lt;/a&gt; (guest relations) to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For parties of 5 or more, Canlis requires a credit card at the time of booking to hold your reservation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy: If not cancelled 48 hours prior to the dining date or in the event of a no show, a fee in the amount of $50 per person will be charged to your credit card.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation. If not reconfirmed your reservation may be given away if need arises&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

